div.p:
Now minde whoſe wiſdom you follow, and whoſe Doctrine you obey;
for you can do Chriſt Ieſus no ſervice in going contrary to his own Doctrine,
though ſome may think they do, Ioh. 16. 2, 3. They shall think they
do God ſervice when they are killing his ſervants, miſtaking them for his
great Enemies, for elſe they would not kill them to do him ſervice.
